    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h4 id=\"安装mysql\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85mysql\" aria-label=\"安装mysql permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装mysql</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>默认可以使用<code class=\"language-text\">apt-get</code>安装：</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> mysql-server</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>初始化配置</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> mysql_secure_installation</code></pre></div>\n<p>配置项挺多，根据需求配置即可。</p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>配置其他用户</li>\n</ol>\n<p>mysql已经将创建账户和赋予权限的方式分开了，需要用两句sql来完成操作：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> mysql -uroot -p\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> </code></pre></div>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85mysql\">安装mysql</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"mysql 安装和学习（基于ubuntu 20）","date":"2019-12-01 08:12","description":"Nginx 安装和学习","type":"Linux使用"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/notebook/linux/mysql/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/notebook/linux/expect/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"